'''磷酸铀酰'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为(UO<sub>2</sub>)<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，存在无水物和多种水合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Radiochemistry|volume=52|issue=2|language=en|issn=1066-3622|date=2010-04|pages=133–137|doi=10.1134/S1066362210020037|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1134/S1066362210020037|title=Synthesis and study of uranyl phosphates (UO2)3(PO4)2·nH2O|accessdate=2021-01-16|author=N. G. Chernorukov, O. V. Nipruk, A. V. Knyazev, Yu. P. Pykhova}}</ref>磷酸铀酰四水合物可由[[硝酸铀酰|硝酸铀酰]]和[[磷酸|磷酸]]在水溶液中（pH~0.5）于70 °C反应制得。<ref name=Yogoubi>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=200|language=en|date=2013-04|pages=13–21|doi=10.1016/j.jssc.2013.01.013|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459613000297|title=Molten salt flux synthesis and crystal structure of a new open-framework uranyl phosphate Cs3(UO2)2(PO4)O2: Spectroscopic characterization and cationic mobility studies|accessdate=2021-01-16|author=S. Yagoubi, C. Renard, F. Abraham, S. Obbade|archive-date=2018-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611174534/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459613000297|dead-url=no}}</ref>其无水物可由UO<sub>2</sub>HPO<sub>4</sub>·4H<sub>2</sub>O在400 °C的热分解得到。<ref name=LV>Kobets, L. V.; Kolevich, T. A.; Savchenko, L. P.; Umpeiko, D. S. Thermal stability of uranyl phosphate tetrahydrate (UO2HPO4.4H2O). ''Koordinatsionnaya Khimiya'', 1975. 1 (4): 499-504. ISSN: 0132-344X</ref>无水物有很强的吸湿性<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Thermochimica Acta|volume=40|issue=3|language=en|date=1980-10|pages=357–365|doi=10.1016/0040-6031(80)80077-3|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0040603180800773|title=The formation and stability of hydrated and anhydrous uranyl phosphates|accessdate=2021-01-16|author=H. Barten, E.H.P. Cordfunke|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625061314/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0040603180800773|dead-url=no}}</ref>；它在900 °C分解得到U<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>。<ref name=LV />

磷酸铀酰四水合物在[[碘化铯|碘化铯]]熔体中于750 °C反应，可以结晶出黄色的Cs<sub>3</sub>(UO<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)O<sub>2</sub>晶体。<ref name=Yogoubi />其水合物在高温下分解，最终产物是U<sub>3</sub>O<sub>8</sub>·U<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>4</sub>。<ref>Kobets, L. V.; Kolevich, T. A.; Umreiko, D. S. Crystal hydrate forms of trisubstituted uranyl orthophosphate. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1978. 23 (4): 909-914. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

它在550 °C可以被[[氢气|氢气]]还原为3UO<sub>2</sub>·P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>，并在750 °C进一步反应，得到[[二氧化铀|UO<sub>2</sub>]]和[[磷|P]]。<ref>Hutter, Jean Claude. Action of hydrogen on phosphates (preparation of phosphorus at low temperature). ''Ann. chim. (Paris)'', 1953. 8: 450-497. CAN48: 2951.</ref>

